transcripts.text: O'er the land of the free and the home of the brave?  Whose broad stripes and bright stars through the perilous fight.  O'er the land of the free and the home of the brave?  Bhagavate vasya di mahi, chaya na pa chodaya.  Om tu vasvaha, Tat Savitur Parayinam Bhago Devasya Di Mahi Joyo Nava Chodaya.  Om Dhuva Svaha Tat Savitur Parayinam Bhago Devasya Di Mahi Joyo Nava Chodaya.  I feel light gliding our way home.  I see a light.  I am alive, in my heart I know, we are alive, together we are whole.  O Achaia Namaha Achaia.  O Achaia Namaha.  O Achaia Namaha Achaia.  O Achaia Namaha.  O Akhaya Naha, Akhaya, O Akhaya Naha.
